nodes.text: The Find Your Equilibrium contest was held annually at the Perpendicular Universe Fair, and was sponsored by three times Xaf award-winning horticultural educator Kaat Thrick-Thrick.

Find Your Equilibrium was mentioned in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
